I89. Homeland defense activities: funds

I11The Secretary of Defense may provide funds to a Governor to employ National Guard units or members to conduct homeland defense activities that the Secretary,\1\N determines to be necessary and appropriate for participation by the National Guard units or members, as the case may be.

